  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About this game</h2>Game QQ group: 576048026<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2>\"Story Of Infinity: Xia\"is A martial arts style Roguelike adventure A·RPG standalone game. According to their own carry different martial arts into the copy, with different weapons, secrets, role growth, to achieve a lively sense of attack through the random fantasy map, explore the background of the whole Reiki world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Core System</h2>There are hundreds of items in the game, including martial arts, weapons, secrets, heritage, treasures, etc., all with unique backstories. Try different combinations, you can play the best of each character, and clear the fantasy more easily.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2>Each character has a different martial arts inclination and story setting, also has a different talent, good use of each character differences, the game can be easier!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/522045e361733f6a35bab6179b1ee1a2.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/88bee19dd63456eda8d0c043d9bcda6f.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Random Map</h2>Each time you enter the Fantasy, the composition of the battle rooms on each floor is random, and sometimes getting through may require a bit of luck.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/01016a9a2b249dc220422cae7fff750e.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/845d119345c6921a60435e7bf526e45a.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/b46ef3fc0d4deddc22e08323545e067c.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapon</h2>Sometimes, having a good weapon is half the battle!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/4082007178cdca3cede090de7f6f6007.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/bc3ef7c544d281176518e95a8e668bb6.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/847f51db8e54704674107d745ea6b3e3.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inheritance</h2>Please carefully choose every martial arts inheritance enhancement, it will directly affect whether you can pass the customs!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/e985880a95f7a7b3309310e01722c367.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/8bf2e355e4de61e42655d0cfa3030ca6.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/37ecb9653bd4d7a146da21566b722cb7.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Secret Book</h2>Collect lots of different items to discover the truth of this world!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/b5b131e78209d53ede8d2127ffcedb5c.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/17bdd8cb4aad0cc3a2261bc1db7e6c7c.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Equipment development</h2>Using dungeon materials to unlock and create equipment can significantly improve the efficiency of exploration<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/bfe4eda88d43958a3008a3c9a081f073.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/801ddb978c969e5f7a9b2d9e039e656c.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/7ad4a949e3395b2dd3712e460a8f266c.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393900/extras/25f22462144059233f2ba15ad530683f.avif?t=1719316022\" width=320 height=180 /></span>",
